  • Constructor Details

    • Schedule

      public Schedule(int sessionId, int movieId, String hallName, LocalDate sessionDate, Time startTime, int vacantSeats)
      Constructor to initialize a movie session schedule.
      Parameters:
      sessionId - The unique identifier for the session.
      movieId - The unique identifier for the movie.
      hallName - The name of the hall where the session is taking place.
      sessionDate - The date when the session is scheduled.
      startTime - The starting time of the session.
      vacantSeats - The number of vacant seats available for the session.
